data.description: Step into your dream home - this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven spanning just under 1300 sqft! This meticulously upgraded gem boasts an open floor plan for effortless living, and a spacious backyard cocooned in privacy. Step inside, and indulge in the allure of clean lines and contemporary aesthetics throughout. Featuring luxurious, slab granite counter tops in the kitchen & bathrooms. Stainless steel appliances and gas cooking elevate the culinary experience, while the neutral color palette sets the stage for sophisticated living. Experience unparalleled convenience with a finished 2-car garage, adorned with painted walls and epoxied flooring, an automatic garage door opener system, and a premium whole-home water purification system ($4000 value).Every detail has been thoughtfully curated for comfort and style. Welcome Home!
